        exits the horizon, the trajectories recombines into a single trajectory. The universe breaks into of order
        <math alttext="k_{1}/k_{0}" class="ltx_Math" display="inline" id="S2.p2.1.m8.1">
         <semantics id="S2.p2.1.m8.1a">
          <mrow id="S2.p2.1.m8.1.6" xref="S2.p2.1.m8.1.6.cmml">
