         </td>
         <td class="ltx_eqn_cell ltx_align_center">
          <math alttext="f_{NL}\sim\frac{\delta\zeta_{k_{1}}}{\zeta_{k_{1}}}\frac{P_{\zeta}^{A}-P_{%
