             f_{NL}\sim\frac{\delta\zeta_{k_{1}}}{\zeta_{k_{1}}}\frac{P_{\zeta}^{A}-P_{%
\zeta}^{B}}{P_{\zeta}^{A}}P_{\zeta}^{-1/2}~{}.
